✅ **Minify & optimize CSS & JavaScript files**.  
✅ **Compress images for faster loading**.  
✅ **Deploy the website using GitHub Pages or Netlify**.  

🎯 **Bonus:** Set up **Google Search Console** to track SEO ranking!  

